Infotainment
[[Image:FoxY-billo.jpg|thumb|[[Bill O'Reilly]] shellfishin out das Infotainment]]
'''Infotainment''' is information and entertainment, woven neatly into a small pill you can take with water. [[LiveJournal]] and its communities have much to offer in the field of infotainment.  Some examples include [http://www.livejournal.com/news.bml news.bml] and the [[ohnotheydidnt]] community.  

[[IRL]] examples include [[Fox]].
